#
# how to open a new instance in notepad++
#
in Notepad++ v6.7.9.2,
Method1. add -multiInst to start notepad++
			notepad++ Target:	"C:\Program Files (x86)\Notepad++\notepad++.exe" -multiInst
		
Method2. set in settings:
			Settings -> Preferences -> Multi-Instance:
				by default, us single instance mode
				always use multiple instances
				open session in new instance

			# ref doc: http://docs.notepad-plus-plus.org/index.php/Multiple_Instances
